      "description": "This 997.1 Carrera S represents a rare opportunity to acquire an analog masterpiece in concours-level condition. The naturally aspirated 3.8L flat-six engine remains in peak factory specification, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule and showing zero oil sweat or bore scoring symptoms. Power is transferred through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with a short-throw shifter, while the Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) system provides telepathic handling. The exterior preserves its original factory clear coat with no road rash, and the interior features pristine leather with no bolster wear or soft-touch plastic degradation. Every VIN tag is present, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it left Zuffenhausen. A turn-key collector-grade example for the discerning driver.",
